The '''Nuba City Spaceport''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] situated to the west of [[Nubia/Legends|Nubia's]] capital, [[Nuba City]]. It was a full-service spaceport, including repair and refueling facilities. The Nuba City monorail had a station there, providing transport into the city.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

